{"tid":796292,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黃洋達: 港獨係「自滅」路線","createTime":"2018-08-27T16:31:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-29T08:41:23.000Z","uid":134071,"like":9,"dislike":71,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"119520faf778afc636e7a8416c007c8221008426","tid":796292,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T16:31:12.000Z","msg":"反左膠先鋒黃洋達既意見, 值得討論一下.<br />\n<br />\n黃洋達: 民主派和黃毓民等反對派被迫使走向港獨, 反對派因此會被大幅邊緣化. 建制派將搶佔「修改基本法, 修憲保護一國兩制」呢個位置, 我地作為制憲派都樂觀其成.  未能見到本土派主動制憲係好遺憾, 但我絕對唔會因此走向「自滅」既港獨路線.<br />\n<br />\n我無連累到黃毓民落選,.  點解黃毓民輸左之餘, 我支持既鄭松泰就贏左?  證明熱血公民既選舉策略有效.<br />\n<br />\n以下節目第四節 (25:00開始)<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/prog/85/1176\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Fprog%2F85%2F1176&d=W4EWNGLU8kWabEt6zhMsOdr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=281ab1b4\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/prog/85/1176</a>"},{"pid":"d8031db33c2d2f5acd3fbee8e6b3d9cf75879c14","tid":796292,"uid":176366,"like":52,"dislike":1,"score":51,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T16:34:07.000Z","msg":"走啦<br />\n過街老鼠"},{"pid":"7d567067ac2cc6b489f2c4b8b46399ce035794cc","tid":796292,"uid":140000,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T17:05:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>反左膠先鋒黃洋達既意見</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c221334d3976cc47f88221e8a5fe949e8ab6747c","tid":796292,"uid":32721,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T17:11:41.000Z","msg":"自己輸左拎蟲太打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f74435476a81942530b621658a234091f58cbb09","tid":796292,"uid":24781,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T17:15:57.000Z","msg":"仲理件垃圾做乜<img src=\"/assets/f